gg.acai.aurora.model

Interface ModelConvertible<M extends Model>

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    NeuralNetwork
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LinearRegression, NeuralNetworkTrainer
    Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public interface ModelConvertible<M extends Model>
    A model convertible represents a class that can be converted to a storable model.

    This is often used in the context of converting a trainable to a model.
